actual_description: If all the rooms are reserved before, the user will be asked to make a choice again.
The price is calculated according to the number of people entering the room.
While calculating the price for Large Deluxe rooms, the number of people is not considered.
It is $ 400 daily in the summer, $ 300 in the spring, and $ 250 in the autumn.
The user must be registered for the first time to the system.
The total price of the reservation depends on the time of year and the type of room.
A 15% discount will be applied on the price calculated when pre-paid reservation is selected.
She must enter 'P' for pre-payment, 'H' for payment with a wire transfer, and 'S' for a standard reservation.
When payment using a wire transfer is selected, if the number of guests exceeds three persons, 50% of 1 guest's fee and 75% of 1 guest's fee will be deducted from the calculated amount.
The types of remaining rooms are Deluxe.
Rates for the deluxe room:$90 per person per night in the summer,$75 in the spring,And $ 50 in the autumn.
There are 100 odd numbered rooms which types are standard, and six even numbered rooms which are large-deluxe.
The room takes up to 4 people.
